<p>Can the object of (TObjectList) know when some values of (TMyObject) was changed?</p>  <p>Some example:</p>  <pre><code>TMyObject = class   oName: string; end;  TMyObjectList = class(TObjectList&lt;TMyObject&gt;) end;  procedure Form1.Button1.Click(Sender: TObject); var   Obj: TMyObject;   List: TMyObjectList; Begin  List:= TMyObjectList.Create;  Obj:= TMyObject.Create;  List.Add(Obj);  List[0].oName:= 'Test'; // here a want to know from var (List) when this object (Obj or List[0]) changed his value.. end; </code></pre>  <p>Thanks for any help.</p>